# MinIO IAM split — memory-server's scoped user.
# ADR-048 PR-B7 (the parser-exploit close).
#
# Username (literal — not a generated secret). Default keeps the
# chart and the bucket-init Job aligned without any override.
#
# 1. Save as ./secrets/minio_audittrace_app_user.txt.
# 2. Run `make k8s-bootstrap-secrets`. Lands at:
#    - Vault: kv/audittrace/minio/audittrace_app (key: username)
#    - k8s Secret: <release>-minio-iam (audittrace_app_user)
audittrace_app
